Study 2

Cleaning and Organizing

Note Here we are using the variable tellegentotal. The summed scores in that column come from pen and paper survey responses, not all of which were broken down and put question-by-question into the data file. This means that we cannot fully reconstruct peoples absorption responses on the question level, but that is ok. We trust the pen and paper totals.

T-Tests

Leland score

Special seeing and hearing Leland subscores

25 participants in the seeing condition answered yes to at least one seeing specific question, whereas only 14 did.

Conversely, 27 people in the hearing condition answered yes to at least on hearing specific question, whereas only 15 people in the seeing condition did.
